# DOCUMENTATION
###############################################################################

Add to design-system.md:

```markdown
## Logo Component

The NaviTrack logo has 3 variants for different contexts:

### Variants

1. **Icon Only** (`variant="icon"`)
   - Use case: Mobile headers, limited space
   - Size: h-12 to h-16
   
2. **Vertical** (`variant="vertical"`)
   - Use case: Login screen, large headers
   - Layout: Icon above text
   - Text: "NAVITRACK" (larger, italic) + "Monitoring Systems" (smaller)
   - Size: h-20 to h-44
   
3. **Horizontal** (`variant="horizontal"`)
   - Use case: Desktop headers, wide viewports
   - Layout: Icon beside text
   - Size: h-12 to h-20

### Usage

```tsx
// Mobile header (icon only)
<Logo variant="icon" className="h-12" />

// Login screen (vertical, large)
<Logo variant="vertical" className="h-20" />

// Desktop header (horizontal)
<Logo variant="horizontal" className="h-16" />
```

### Styling Rules

- Logo works on glass backgrounds
- Maintains visibility in light/dark themes
- Uses primary brand color (#2d8a3e)
- Responsive sizing via className
- No inline styles
```

